[new:AlexSchroeder:2013-04-24 13:33 UTC]
Ok, I've been postponing this [[2013-02-18|for the longest time]]. Time to take the plunge!
I activated the "bootstrap" using configuration for EmacsWiki.
If you're interested, the bootstrap-specific changes are mostly in [http://emacswiki.org/emacs/emacs-bootstrap.js emacs-bootstrap.js] and [http://emacswiki.org/css/bootstrap.css bootstrap.css].
*Evgkeni Sampelnikof* did most of the design once I had the initial framework in place. Thanks!

If you don't like the new design, here's how to control the cookie:

* http://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/2013-04-24?bootstrap=0 -- disable
* http://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/2013-04-24?bootstrap=1 -- enable (the default)

Any changes you want to suggest, email me at kensanata@gmail.com, or leave a comment on the [[Comments on 2013-04-24|Talk]] page. :)
